  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.scenes.scene2d.utils.Layout, Movable
    public class Dish
extends ImageMovable
    Dishes are used to serve Ingredients. They interact with Ingredient's Ingredient.fry() and Ingredient.getFryingProgress() methods. This class extends Station. Recipes are stored as an ArrayList of Ingredients.
